<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FF4F6AF0FA4B905C178ABD7F" pageId="180" pageNumber="942" type="conservation">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFF4F6AF0FA4B905C178ABD7F" blockId="180.[1461,2669,720,1692]" pageId="180" pageNumber="942">
<emphasis id="F6E0EAECFF4F6AF0FA4B905C1914BD14" bold="true" box="[1463,1812,1541,1574]" pageId="180" pageNumber="942">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Least Concern on The IUCN Red List. The Montane 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF4F6AF0FA0190751857BD7F" authority="Kaup, 1829" box="[1533,1623,1580,1613]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Myotis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="180" pageNumber="942" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Myotis</taxonomicName>
is widespread and tolerates habitat alterations by humans.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
